testSave1.sql1: SELECT BIN_PrtCatPropertyID AS propId, PropertyNameChinese AS propNameCN, PropertyNameForeign AS propNameEN, TeminalFlag AS teminalFlag, ViewSeq AS viewSeq FROM Basis.BIN_PrtCatProperty WHERE BIN_OrganizationInfoID = 1 AND BIN_BrandInfoID = 3  AND ValidFlag = '1' AND PropertyNameChinese = '测试分类4'
